{"customEmbed": {"name": "MI CLEAN HTML 5", "enabled": true, "loadOnce": false, "position": "BODY_END", "embedData": {"category": "ESSENTIAL", "html": "<!-- X\u0130DM\u018fTL\u018fR -->\n<section class=\"sec\" id=\"xidmetler\">\n  <div class=\"sec-top rv\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:14px\"><span class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"display:inline-flex;margin:0\">Professional</span> <span class=\"tag\">15 Xidm\u0259t N\u00f6v\u00fc</span></div>\n      <h2 class=\"h2\"><b>Professional</b><br>Xidm\u0259tl\u0259r</h2>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"sec-desc\">Konsultasiyadan audit\u0259, dozaj qura\u015fd\u0131rmadan HACCP plana \u2014 sat\u0131\u015fdan sonra da yan\u0131n\u0131zday\u0131q.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"svc-grid rv\">\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83d\udd2c</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Texniki Konsultasiya</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">Otelin tam ehtiyac analizi, m\u0259hsul se\u00e7imi. T\u0259l\u0259b siyah\u0131s\u0131 + uy\u011funluq matrisas\u0131 haz\u0131rlan\u0131r.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">1\u20133 g\u00fcn</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Pulsuz</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\u2699\ufe0f</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Dozaj Sistemi Qura\u015fd\u0131rma</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">Cama\u015f\u0131rxana &amp; m\u0259tb\u0259x \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn dozaj pompas\u0131. Qura\u015fd\u0131rma akt\u0131 + kalibrasiya.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">1 g\u00fcn</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Layih\u0259 \u00fczr\u0259</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83d\udc65</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Housekeeping T\u0259limi</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">Kimy\u0259vi t\u0259hl\u00fck\u0259sizlik, d\u00fczg\u00fcn istifad\u0259, zona r\u0259ng kodlama. Sertifikat + test n\u0259tic\u0259si.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">2\u20134 saat</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Per session</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83d\udccb</div><div class=\"svc-name\">SDS / Etiket Paketi</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">Safety Data Sheet toplanmas\u0131, etiketl\u0259r, piktogramlar haz\u0131rlanmas\u0131.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">3\u20137 g\u00fcn</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Layih\u0259 \u00fczr\u0259</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83c\udf7d\ufe0f</div><div class=\"svc-name\">HACCP Gigiyena Plan\u0131</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">M\u0259tb\u0259x sanitizasiya plan\u0131, yoxlama checklistl\u0259ri. HACCP uy\u011fun SOP s\u0259n\u0259di.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">5\u201310 g\u00fcn</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Layih\u0259 \u00fczr\u0259</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83d\udcca</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Cama\u015f\u0131rxana Audit</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">Su s\u0259rtliyi, dozaj, yuma keyfiyy\u0259ti analizi. Hesabat + optimizasiya plan\u0131.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">3\u20135 g\u00fcn</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Layih\u0259 \u00fczr\u0259</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83e\uddea</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Pilot / Trial Proqram\u0131</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">Se\u00e7ilmi\u015f m\u0259hsullar\u0131n 2\u20134 h\u0259ft\u0259lik s\u0131naq t\u0259tbiqi. Test protokolu + hesabat.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">2\u20134 h\u0259ft\u0259</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Paket</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83c\udf3f</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Eco Alternativl\u0259r Se\u00e7imi</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">Safer Choice/eco variantlar\u0131n se\u00e7imi, uy\u011funluq matrisas\u0131. Sertifikat s\u0259n\u0259di.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">3\u20135 g\u00fcn</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Paket</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83d\udce6</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Anbar Optimalla\u015fd\u0131rma</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">MOQ, t\u0259hl\u00fck\u0259sizlik stok, sifari\u015f d\u00f6vr\u00fcn\u00fcn qurulmas\u0131. Min-max plan haz\u0131rlan\u0131r.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">3\u20137 g\u00fcn</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Layih\u0259 \u00fczr\u0259</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83d\ude9b</div><div class=\"svc-name\">\u00c7atd\u0131r\u0131lma &amp; Logistika</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">\u00c7atd\u0131r\u0131lma qrafiki, b\u00f6l\u00fcnm\u00fc\u015f \u00e7atd\u0131r\u0131lma, q\u0259bul protokolu. Daimi ayl\u0131q servis.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">Daimi</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Ayl\u0131q</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\u2705</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Keyfiyy\u0259t Z\u0259man\u0259ti &amp; SLA</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">M\u0259hsul q\u00fcsurlar\u0131 \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn SLA, d\u0259yi\u015fm\u0259 qaydas\u0131. Reklamasiya formas\u0131 haz\u0131r.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">1\u20132 g\u00fcn SLA</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Daxildir</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"svc\"><div class=\"svc-ico\">\ud83c\udfa8</div><div class=\"svc-name\">Logo \u00c7ap &amp; Dizayn</div><div class=\"svc-desc\">Salfet, amenities, qabla\u015fd\u0131rma \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn brend \u00e7ap\u0131. Print-ready fayl + mockup.</div><div class=\"svc-tags\"><span class=\"svc-tag\">7\u201320 g\u00fcn</span><span class=\"svc-tag\">Layih\u0259 \u00fczr\u0259</span></div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- WHY + STEPS -->\n<section class=\"sec sec-cream\">\n  <div class=\"eyebrow rv\" style=\"color:#A07840;margin-bottom:28px\">Niy\u0259 MI CLEAN GROUP?</div>\n  <div class=\"why-grid rv\">\n    <div class=\"why\"><div class=\"why-ico\">\ud83c\udfc6</div><div class=\"why-name\">5 Ulduz Standart\u0131</div><div class=\"why-desc\">HACCP, ISO, Safer Choice standartlar\u0131na uy\u011fun b\u00fct\u00fcn m\u0259hsullar.</div></div>\n    <div class=\"why\"><div class=\"why-ico\">\ud83e\uddfe</div><div class=\"why-name\">SDS Sertifikat</div><div class=\"why-desc\">H\u0259r m\u0259hsul SDS + INCI list s\u0259n\u0259di il\u0259 \u00e7atd\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r.</div></div>\n    <div class=\"why\"><div class=\"why-ico\">\u267b\ufe0f</div><div class=\"why-name\">Eco Alternativl\u0259r</div><div class=\"why-desc\">B\u00fct\u00fcn kimy\u0259vinin Safer Choice eco versiyas\u0131 m\u00f6vcuddur.</div></div>\n    <div class=\"why\"><div class=\"why-ico\">\ud83d\ude9a</div><div class=\"why-name\">5\u20137 G\u00fcn \u00c7atd\u0131r\u0131lma</div><div class=\"why-desc\">Bak\u0131 v\u0259 \u0259traf regionlar. B\u00f6l\u00fcnm\u00fc\u015f \u00e7atd\u0131r\u0131lma m\u00fcmk\u00fcnd\u00fcr.</div></div>\n    <div class=\"why\"><div class=\"why-ico\">\ud83c\udf81</div><div class=\"why-name\">Pulsuz Pilot</div><div class=\"why-desc\">2\u20134 h\u0259ft\u0259lik pulsuz / endiriml\u0259 s\u0131naq. \u00d6nc\u0259 s\u0131nay\u0131n.</div></div>\n    <div class=\"why\"><div class=\"why-ico\">\ud83e\udd1d</div><div class=\"why-name\">Tam D\u0259st\u0259k</div><div class=\"why-desc\">Konsultasiyadan audit\u0259 \u2014 \u00e7atd\u0131r\u0131lmadan sonra da yan\u0131n\u0131zday\u0131q.</div></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"eyebrow rv\" style=\"color:#A07840;margin:56px 0 22px\">Nec\u0259 sifari\u015f etm\u0259k olar?</div>\n  <div class=\"steps rv\">\n    <div class=\"step\"><div class=\"step-n\">01</div><div class=\"step-t\">\u018flaq\u0259 Saxlay\u0131n</div><div class=\"step-d\">Email, WhatsApp v\u0259 ya telefon vasit\u0259sil\u0259 t\u0259l\u0259b siyah\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 g\u00f6nd\u0259rin.</div></div>\n    <div class=\"step\"><div class=\"step-n\">02</div><div class=\"step-t\">Qiym\u0259t T\u0259klifi Al\u0131n</div><div class=\"step-d\">24 saat \u0259rzind\u0259 f\u0259rdi qiym\u0259t. Pilot se\u00e7imi m\u00f6vcuddur.</div></div>\n    <div class=\"step\"><div class=\"step-n\">03</div><div class=\"step-t\">Sifari\u015fi T\u0259sdiqliy\u0131n</div><div class=\"step-d\">Raz\u0131l\u0131q sonras\u0131 m\u00fcqavil\u0259 imzalan\u0131r. Proses\u0259 ba\u015flan\u0131r.</div></div>\n    <div class=\"step\"><div class=\"step-n\">04</div><div class=\"step-t\">5\u20137 G\u00fcnd\u0259 \u00c7atd\u0131r\u0131lma</div><div class=\"step-d\">\u0130\u015f g\u00fcn\u00fc hesab\u0131. Q\u0259bul akt\u0131 verilir.</div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- CONTACT -->\n"}}}